Package iaik.x509.attr

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttCertIssuer
    Represents an attribute certificate issuer.
    TargetChecker
    Interface to may be implemented for application-dependent checking if some server/service is a valid target/proxy of an attribute certificate that contains the TargetInformation or ProxyInfo extension.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ACRL
    This class represents a X.509v2 CertificateRevocationList (CRL) for Attribute Certificates (ACRL).
    AttributeCertificate
    This class represents an attribute certificate, as specified by the PKIX Internet Attribute Certificate Profile for Authorization.
    AttributeCertificateExtensions
    Extends class X509Extensions for registering and handling Attribute certificate extensions.
    Holder
    This class implements the AC type Holder.
    IssuerSerial
    This class implements the AC type IssuerSerial.
    ObjectDigestInfo
    This class implements the AC type ObjectDigestInfo.
    RevokedAttributeCertificate
    This class represents a revoked attribute certificate.
    SecurityCategory
    This class is the basic implementation for the SecurityCategory type as specified by the X.509 Attribute Certificate profile (RFC 5755) to maybe used within a Clearance attribute for providing further authorization information.
    Target
    This class implements the Target type specified by the X.509 Attribute Certificate profile (RFC 5755) to be used within TargetInformation or ProxyInfo attribute certificate extensions.
    TargetCert
    This class implements the TargetCert type specified by the X.509 Attribute Certificate profile (RFC 5755) to be used within TargetInformation or ProxyInfo attribute certificate extensions.
    TargetGroup
    This class implements the TargetGroup type specified by the X.509 Attribute Certificate profile (RFC 5755) to be used within TargetInformation or ProxyInfo attribute certificate extensions.
    TargetName
    This class implements the TargetName type specified by the X.509 Attribute Certificate profile (RFC 5755) to be used within TargetInformation or ProxyInfo attribute certificate extensions.
    Targets
    This class implements the Targets type specified by the X.509 Attribute Certificate profile (RFC 5755) to be used within TargetInformation or ProxyInfo attribute certificate extensions.
    UnknownSecurityCategory
    This class implements any unknown SecurityCategory value.
    V1Form
    This class implements the AC type V1Form.
    V2Form
    This class implements the AC type V2Form.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TargetException
    Exception to be thrown if a Target implementation is not be able to determine if a given server/service is a target for the attribute certificate that contains the particular Target extension.
